01:37:54,015 --> 01:37:56,685
that overhead giving
the game near bare

1875
01:37:56,684 --> 01:37:59,984
to the metal access
to the power of A7.

1876
01:37:59,988 --> 01:38:05,728
The results are stunning up
to 10x faster draw call rates.

1877
01:38:05,727 --> 01:38:11,467
Now, in addition to these
dramatically reduced overheads,

1878
01:38:11,466 --> 01:38:13,236
you get access not
just to graphics

