01:38:13,234 --> 01:38:16,204
but to the compute
power of the GPU,

1880
01:38:16,204 --> 01:38:18,544
and Metal supports
pre-compiled shaders

1881
01:38:18,539 --> 01:38:19,939
and efficient multithreading

1882
01:38:19,941 --> 01:38:23,111
so you can always get the
most out of the processor.

